ns.\n\r','',1,0,3,100,100,0),(1023,5268,'A small ugly cave','You see a small cave.  Skeletons of many types of creatures litter the area.\n\rObviously, no fox lives here!  The oppression makes you want to leave and\n\rvomit.\n\r','',1,0,3,100,100,0),(1024,5269,'A small ugly cave','You are in a small ugly cave.  More skeletons lie around.  It is obvious\n\rthat the owner doesn\'t want you here.  The exit north is still visible.\n\rSome writings are on this wall.\n\r','',1,0,3,100,100,0),(1025,5270,'Down the path into a dead end','You are down the path.  There is no obvious exit in this place, exit the\n\rone back up north.  All around you, you see skeletons.\n\r','',1,0,3,100,100,0),(1026,5271,'The Valley in the dark dwarf forest','You are in a valley in the forest.  To the north is a trail out of this\n\rdark valley.  South is more of this valley.\n\r','',1,0,3,100,100,0),(1027,5272,'A dim trail in the dwarf forest','You are in a dim trail in the dwarf forest.  Not much light passes through\n\rhere.  To the south is a gloomy valley, while to the north the light grows\n\rbrighter.\n\r','',1,0,3,100,100,0),(1028,5273,'A dim trail in the dwarf forest','You are in a dim trail in the dwarf forest.  Not much light passes through\n\rhere.  The trail runs north and south, and the light seems to come from the\n\rnorth.  To the east, you see a small path into darkness.\n\r','',0,0,3,100,100,0),(1029,5274,'A dim trail in the dwarf forest','You are in a dim trail in the dwarf forest.  Not much light passes through\n\rhere.  The trail runs north and south, and the light seems to come from the\n\rnorth.\n\r','',0,0,3,100,100,0),(1030,5275,'A bend in the dim trail in the dwarf forest','You are in a dim trail in the dwarf forest.  Not much light passes through\n\rhere.  The trail runs south and west.  The trail west looks much friendlier\n\rthan the one leading south.\n\r','',0,0,3,100,100,0),(1031,5276,'A trail in the dwarf forest','You are in a trail in the dwarf forest.  The trees are stunted and it\n\rlooks dry around here.  The trail leads east and west.  It looks dimmer to\n\rthe east.\n\r','',0,0,3,100,100,0),(1032,5277,'A trail in the dwarf forest','You are in a trail in the dwarf forest.  The trees are stunted and it\n\rlooks dry around here.  The trail leads east and west.\n\r','',0,0,3,100,100,0),(1033,5278,'A trail in the dwarf forest','You are in a trail in the dwarf forest.  The trees are stunted and it\n\rlooks dry around here.  The trail leads east and west.\n\r','',0,0,3,100,100,0),(1034,5279,'The bend in the trail in the dwarf forest','You are in a bend in the trail in the forest.  The trees are stunted, but\n\rnot so dry around here.  The trail leads east, and to the south, you see a\n\rwaterfall.\n\r','',0,0,3,100,100,0),(1035,5280,'A dark bend in the forest','You are in a dark bend in the forest.  To the west, you see the trail\n\rleading back to the dwarven forest, and to the south, you see a dark and\n\rdismal path.\n\r','',0,0,3,100,100,0),(1036,5281,'By the beautiful waterfall','You see a VERY beautiful waterfall here.  It looks almost as if diamonds are\n\rfalling down the mountain.  (You reach out and grab and no, it IS only water.)\n\rIt looks so nice here, you feel like taking a nap.\n\rThe trail leads north and south.\n\r','',0,0,4,100,100,0),(1037,6500,'Path to Dwarven Village','All around you are the mountains of the southern range, home of dwarves and \n\rgiants.  You can climb back down the mountains to the west and leave these \n\rrealms, or seek riches in the northern mineshafts.  A dirt road leads south, \n\rtowards a small building.  You can hear crying and shrieking coming from it.\n\r','',0,0,2,100,100,0),(1038,6501,'Path, base of mountain','Now you are at the bottom of a rugged mountain.  The forest around you is\n\rvery dense, and it seems very dark to the north.\n\r','',0,0,4,100,100,0),(1039,6502,'Path, middle of mountain','Standing on the middle of the mountain, you can easily see the turning\n\rpoint to the south, and the top of the mountain is very near to the north.\n\r','',0,0,5,100,100,0),(1040,6503,'Top of mountain','You are now on the top of the mountain.  To the south you see a path\n\rleading down the mountain.  To the east and west you see entrances to\n\rwhat seems like mines.\n\r','',0,0,4,100,100,0),(1041,6504,'Narrow Path','This is a narrow path leading to the Dwarven Kingdom.  It looks less\n\rtravelled than the others, and it is very creepy.  The path opens up\n\rto the south, and continues to the north.\n\r','',8,0,0,100,100,0),(1042,6505,'Entrance to Mountain','Here is an entrance to the mountain.  The door looks very well built,\n\rand you can hear noise coming from within.\n\r','',0,0,2,100,100,0),(1043,6506,'Bend in Narrow Path','This is a narrow path that bends to the east here.  The trees hang over\n\rthe path, and it is very overgrown.  The narrow path continues to the\n\rsouth and to the east.\n\r','',8,0,0,100,100,0),(1044,6507,'Narrow path','This path is very narrow, and it continues to the north and west.\n\r','',8,0,0,100,100,0),(1045,6508,'Narrow north-south path','This path leads to the north and south.  To the north you can see a\n\rdoor, and to the south the path continues.\n\r','',8,0,0,100,100,0),(1046,6509,'Door to Kingdom','Here the path turns to the west.  You can see a door in front of you,\n\rand the path continues to the west and south.\n\r','',8,0,0,100,100,0),(1047,6510,'Path to the Castle','You are on a path that will eventually lead to the castle.  It\n\rcontinues north to the castle, and there is a door on the western wall.\n\r','',8,0,0,100,100,0),(1048,6511,'Still on the path to the Castle','You are still on the path to the castle, or back to the\n\rDwarven village, whichever way you wish to go.  The path\n\rcontinues to the north and south.\n\r','',8,0,0,100,100,0),(1049,6512,'Door to Castle','Here there is a door to the castle to the east.  The castle\n\ris elegantly designed, and looks much like a roll of toilet paper\n\rstanding on end.  A sign says:\n\r\n\r              ******************************************\n\r              *  WELCOME TO THE CASTLE OF STRANGELOVE  *\n\r              *      Here, celibacy is uninvited       *\n\r              ******************************************\n\r','',8,0,0,100,100,0),(1050,6513,'Inside the entrance','Everything here is covered in soot and very grimy.  The path continues\n\rto the east and north, and there is a door to the west.\n\r','',8,0,0,100,100,0),(1051,6514,'Path','You are on a path in the dwarven village which leads north to the shops\n\rand south to the corner of the area.\n\r','',8,0,0,100,100,0),(1052,6515,'Turn in road','You are on a path that leads to a Hide & Tooth shop to the west, and the\n\rpath continues to the south.\n\r','',8,0,0,100,100,0),(1053,6516,'Hide & Tooth Shop','You are in the Hide & Tooth shop.  Here you may buy the finest in Dwarven\n\rweapons and armors. The path continues to the north and east.\n\r','',8,0,0,100,100,0),(1054,6517,'Path to the north of shop','You are on a path to the north of the Hide & Tooth shop.  The path continues\n\rto the north, and there is Granite Head\'s bakery to the west.\n\r','',8,0,0,100,100,0),(1055,6518,'North of Shops','Here the path bends to the east towards the barracks. To the\n\rsouth you can see the shops.\n\r','',8,0,0,100,100,0),(1056,6519,'Path by Hospital','Here the path passes by the Hospital to the north.  It continues\n\rto the east to the barracks, and to the west.\n\r','',8,0,0,100,100,0),(1057,6520,'Path next to barracks','Here the path continues west, and east to the barracks.\n\r','',8,0,0,100,100,0),(1058,6521,'Entrance to barracks','Here there is an entrance to the barracks to the south, and\n\rthe path continues to the west.\n\r','',8,0,0,100,100,0),(1059,6522,'Guard House','You are in the guard house to the west of the entrance\n\rto the castle.  There are nude posters covering the walls.\n\r','',8,0,0,100,100,0),(1060,6523,'First Barrac