ortal is hovering in the air just in front of the east wall.\n\r','',524,0,0,100,100,0),(2551,6903,'Quifael\'s virtual balcony','You are on a transparent balcony hanging in mid-air.  You notice a faint blue\n\rglow surrounding everything, even yourself, making it seem as transparent as\n\rthe balcony itself.  From here, you have a terrific view of the whole Forest\n\rof Haon-Dor.\n\rA transparent bronze plate has been bolted to the balcony railing.\n\rA magical portal is hovering in the air to the west.\n\r','',520,0,0,100,100,0),(2552,6904,'Quifael\'s hall','You are in sparsely decorated and quite dusty hall.  Old wooden doors lead\n\rnorth, east and south and to the west is the front door.\n\rAn old mirror hangs on the wall.\n\r','',520,0,0,100,100,0),(2553,6905,'Quifael\'s kitchen','You are in an old-fashioned kitchen.\n\r','',520,0,0,100,100,0),(2554,7001,'The muddy sewer','You are standing in mud to your knees. This is not the kind of place\n\rfor a picnic. The muddy sewer stretches further into the south.\n\r','',9,0,5,100,100,0),(2555,7002,'The muddy sewer junction','The muddy sewer stretches into the dark to the south. It looks as if \n\rno person has ever sat his foot here before. It\'s too muddy for that\n\ranyway. The sewer leads north, south and east from here.\n\r','',9,0,5,100,100,0),(2556,7003,'The mudhole','You stand in mud all the way up to your thighs and it\'s not too \n\rcomfortable since you are used to a somewhat different environment.\n\rThe sewer leads to the north of here. In the middle you can just make\n\rout an enormous drainpipe leading down.\n\r','',13,0,5,100,100,0),(2557,7004,'The Dark Pit','You are standing by the edge of a dark pit that leads down into even\n\rdeeper darkness. >BWWAAADDRR< - The smell from down there is unbearable.\n\rThe sewer stretches into the darkness to the east.\n\r','',9,0,0,100,100,0),(2558,7005,'The muddy sewer','You are standing in the middle of a bend of the sewer pipe. It is very\n\rdark around here and 